<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<I>by suki</I> -- I found this online somewhere:<P>1] Don't let the Wizards Die [they deal the damage].<BR>2] Don't let the Druids Die [the wizards might need them for an escape].<BR>3] Don't let the Shaman's Die [see #2]<BR>4] Don't let the Clerics's Die [they are keeping you alive so you can keep the Wizards alive].<BR>5] Don't let the Wizards die [worth mentioning again].<BR>6] Don't let the other tank[s] die [then YOU'LL be taking ALL the punishment, will die faster, and then the wizards will die].<BR>7] Ignore #6 if it's a stinky Ogre Shadow Knight who threatens to eat any of above mentioned party members.<BR>8]Don't let the Wizards die [yes, again].<BR>9] Don't Die [unless your death will save a wizard ].<BR>10] If all else fails, well your dead anyways, your a tank, get used to it.<P> <IMG SRC="tongue.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Wizards are like steak and potatoes and red wine.  Druids are fruit baskets :)<P>http://www.graffe.com
</FONT>
