<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Hehee sounds like suki there overburns... either that or this is a pre-kunark commandment list   <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>Seriously, unless they've seriously pissed them off, a tank isnt going to LET someone die.<P>Here's my list =)<P>1. Taunt before breaking Mez.<BR>2. Dont switch targets mid-fight unless you have a VERY good reason.<BR>3. Dont wait until clerics go OOM CH'ing before you call for the damn assist.<BR>4. Always go after unmezzable targets first. Take down casters before melees if you have no mezzer.<BR>5. STAY CLOSE to the mob to keep hate up.<BR>6. If you're summoned, make sure you fall back into formation properly. <BR>7. Dont position yourself so that the push backs the mob directly into a wall, or off a cliff.<BR>8. Turn off your attack and/or turn away when the target becomes ENRAGED.<BR>9. Disarm generates a little hate too =)<BR>10. Be a Gnome. Gnome Power!
</FONT>
